  "body": "Pre-Merge I used to run lighthouse in two terminal tabs, one `lighthouse bn --staking` tab and and one `lighthouse vc` tab.\r\n\r\nThe Handbook has a special section for Post-Merge setup, it explicitly states that\r\n\r\n```\r\nlighthouse \\\r\n    --network mainnet \\\r\n    beacon_node \\\r\n    --http \\\r\n    --eth1-endpoints http://localhost:8545,https://TOKEN@eth2-beacon-mainnet.infura.io\r\n```\r\n\r\nshould be migrated to:\r\n\r\n```\r\nlighthouse \\\r\n    --network mainnet \\\r\n    beacon_node \\\r\n    --http \\\r\n    --execution-endpoint http://localhost:8551\r\n    --execution-jwt ~/.ethereum/geth/jwtsecret\r\n```\r\n\r\nI guess this is what I've previously used `lighthouse bn --staking` for.\r\n\r\nBut what is the recommended new command for `lighthouse -vc`? Is it not needed anymore?\r\n",
