    "body": "I've updated the docs in this PR: https://github.com/sigp/lighthouse/pull/3509\r\n\r\nRegarding the fee recipient: 0x-prefix or no prefix will both work. Quotes are fine if you're running in a shell as the shell will strip them. In general, avoid quotes as Lighthouse won't parse them, and won't work if they're passed through verbatim from a `docker-compose` config, etc.",
